#

Spicy Shrimp and Avocado Burrito

$12.99
600 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

shellfishdairy

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freehigh-protein

Tags:

shrimpavocadoburritospicy

Description

A zesty and satisfying burrito packed with spicy shrimp, creamy avocado, and fresh veggies wrapped in a soft tortilla.

Ingredients

  • large shrimp: 1 lb
  • avocado: 1 large
  • whole wheat tortillas: 4
  • black beans: 1 can
  • fresh cilantro: 1/4 cup
  • lime juice: 2 tbsp
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • cumin: 1 tsp
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • sour cream: 1/2 cup
